How To Play **GTPS** Using Host Go
Download Host Go, Link :
https://apkpure.com/id/no-root-hosts-go/dns.hosts.server.change
Open Host Go. Then Press Host Editor.

Press [+]. Then Add IP Address And Domain.

**
IP Address : 103.250.10.160
Domain : www.growtopia1.com
IP Address : 103.250.10.160
Domain : www.growtopia2.com**

After adding IP & Domain you must click START to start playing
